🎮 The Gaming Divide: PC Gaming vs. Console Gaming vs. Mobile Gaming

Situation: You’ve saved up for a gaming setup — but where should your investment go?
Debate: Which platform offers the best overall gaming experience?

🖥️ Team PC: “Customization, performance, and modding.”

🎮 Team Console: “Exclusives, plug-and-play simplicity, and stability.”

📱 Team Mobile: “Accessibility, affordability, and massive player base.”
